 the original order was created."}, "refund_created_at": {"type": "timestamp without time zone", "index": 11, "name": "refund_created_at", "comment": "The timestamp when the refund was created."}, "refund_processed_at": {"type": "timestamp without time zone", "index": 12, "name": "refund_processed_at", "comment": "The timestamp when the refund was processed."}, "is_processed": {"type": "boolean", "index": 13, "name": "is_processed", "comment": "Whether the refund has been processed (i.e. processed_at is not null)."}, "days_to_refund": {"type": "integer", "index": 14, "name": "days_to_refund", "comment": "Number of days between the original order creation date and the refund creation date."}, "refund_note": {"type": "text", "index": 15, "name": "refund_note", "comment": "An optional note attached to the refund by the merchant or staff."}, "staff_user_id": {"type": "bigint", "index": 16, "name": "staff_user_id", "comment": "The ID of the staff member who processed the refund."}, "product_id": {"type": "bigint", "index": 17, "name": "product_id", "comment": "The ID of the product associated with the refunded line item."}, "variant_id": {"type": "bigint", "index": 18, "name": "variant_id", "comment": "The ID of the product variant associated with the refunded line item."}, "product_title": {"type": "text", "index": 19, "name": "product_title", "comment": "The title of the product at the time of the original order."}, "sku": {"type": "text", "index": 20, "name": "sku", "comment": "The SKU of the product variant at the time of the original order."}, "vendor": {"type": "text", "index": 21, "name": "vendor", "comment": "The vendor of the product at the time of the original order."}, "original_unit_price": {"type": "double precision", "index": 22, "name": "original_unit_price", "comment": "The unit price of the product at the time of the original order (in shop currency)."}, "is_gift_card": {"type": "boolean", "index": 23, "name": "is_gift_card", "comment": "Whether the refunded line item was a gift card."}, "refunded_quantity": {"type": "integer", "index": 24, "name": "refunded_quantity", "comment": "The quantity of items refunded on this line item."}, "subtotal": {"type": "integer", "index": 25, "name": "subtotal", "comment": "The subtotal of the refund for this line item, before tax (in shop currency)."}, "total_tax": {"type": "double precision", "index": 26, "name": "total_tax", "comment": "The total tax refunded for this line item (in shop currency)."}, "total_refunded": {"type": "double precision", "index": 27, "name": "total_refunded", "comment": "The total amount refunded for this line item, including tax (in shop currency). Equal to subtotal + total_tax."}, "restock_type": {"type": "text", "index": 28, "name": "restock_type", "comment": "How the refunded item was restocked. One of 'return', 'cancel', 'legacy_restock', or 'no_restock'."}, "restock_location_id": {"type": "bigint", "index": 29, "name": "restock_location_id", "comment": "The ID of the location where the item was restocked, if applicable."}, "is_restocked": {"type": "boolean", "index": 30, "name": "is_restocked", "comment": "Whether the item was physically restocked (restock_type is 'return', 'cancel', or 'legacy_restock')."}, "is_restock_only": {"type": "boolean", "index": 31, "name": "is_restock_only", "comment": "Whether this refund line had no financial value and only restocked inventory (subtotal and total_tax are both zero and the item was restocked)."}}, "stats": {"has_stats": {"id": "has_stats", "label": "Has Stats?", "value": false, "include": false, "description": "Indicates whether there are statistics for this table"}}, "unique_id": "model.shopify.shopify__refund_lines"}, "model.shopify.shopify__refunds": {"metadata": {"type": "BASE TABLE", "schema": "public_shopify", "name": "shopify__refunds", "database": "postgres", "comment": "Each record represents a refund transaction. Aggregates line item financials to the refund grain and includes discrepancy ad