ry item's weight."}, "is_tracked_editable_locked": {"type": "boolean", "index": 27, "name": "is_tracked_editable_locked", "comment": "Indicates whether the 'tracked' field for the inventory item is locked from editing."}, "tracked_editable_reason": {"type": "text", "index": 28, "name": "tracked_editable_reason", "comment": "Provides the reason why the 'tracked' field for the inventory item is locked from editing."}, "location_name": {"type": "text", "index": 29, "name": "location_name", "comment": "The name of the location."}, "is_location_deleted": {"type": "boolean", "index": 30, "name": "is_location_deleted", "comment": "Boolean representing whether the record was soft-deleted in Shopify."}, "is_location_active": {"type": "boolean", "index": 31, "name": "is_location_active", "comment": "Boolean representing whether the location is active. If true, then the location can be used to sell products, stock inventory, and fulfill orders.\n"}, "address_1": {"type": "text", "index": 32, "name": "address_1", "comment": "The location's street address."}, "address_2": {"type": "text", "index": 33, "name": "address_2", "comment": "The optional second line of the location's street address."}, "city": {"type": "text", "index": 34, "name": "city", "comment": "The city the location is in."}, "country": {"type": "text", "index": 35, "name": "country", "comment": "The country the location is in (two-letter code)."}, "country_code": {"type": "text", "index": 36, "name": "country_code", "comment": "The two-letter code (ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 format) corresponding to country the location is in."}, "country_name": {"type": "text", "index": 37, "name": "country_name", "comment": "The name of the country where the inventory level is located."}, "is_legacy_location": {"type": "boolean", "index": 38, "name": "is_legacy_location", "comment": "Boolean representing whether this is a fulfillment service location. If true, then the location is a fulfillment service location.  If false, then the location was created by the merchant and isn't tied to a fulfillment service.\n"}, "province": {"type": "text", "index": 39, "name": "province", "comment": "The province, state, or district of the location."}, "province_code": {"type": "text", "index": 40, "name": "province_code", "comment": "The province, state, or district code (ISO 3166-2 alpha-2 format) of the location."}, "phone": {"type": "character varying", "index": 41, "name": "phone", "comment": "The phone number of the location. This value can contain special characters, such as - or +."}, "zip": {"type": "integer", "index": 42, "name": "zip", "comment": "The zip or postal code."}, "location_created_at": {"type": "timestamp without time zone", "index": 43, "name": "location_created_at", "comment": "The date and time (ISO 8601 format) when the location was created."}, "location_updated_at": {"type": "timestamp without time zone", "index": 44, "name": "location_updated_at", "comment": "The date and time (ISO 8601 format) when the location was last updated."}, "variant_id": {"type": "integer", "index": 45, "name": "variant_id", "comment": "The unique numeric identifier for the product variant."}, "product_id": {"type": "integer", "index": 46, "name": "product_id", "comment": "The unique numeric identifier for the product."}, "variant_title": {"type": "text", "index": 47, "name": "variant_title", "comment": "The title of the product variant. The title field is a concatenation of the option1, option2, and option3 fields. You can only update title indirectly using the option fields."}, "variant_inventory_policy": {"type": "text", "index": 48, "name": "variant_inventory_policy", "comment": "Whether customers are allowed to place an order for the product variant when it's out of stock."}, "variant_price": {"type": "double precision", "index": 49, "name": "variant_price", "comment": "The price of the product variant in shop currency."}, "variant_media_id": {"type": "integer", "index": 50, "name": "variant_media_id", "comment": "The unique numeric identifier for a product variant's media."}, "is_variant_taxable": {"type": "boolean", "index": 51, "name": "is_variant_taxable", "comment": "Whether a tax is charged when the product variant is sold."}, "variant_barcode": {"type": "text", "index": 52, "name": "variant_barcode", "comment": "The barcode, UPC, or ISBN number for the product."}, "variant_inventory_quantity": {"type": "integer", "index": 53, "name": "variant_inventory_quantity", "comment": "An aggregate of inventory across all locations. To adjust inventory at a specific location, use the InventoryLevel resource."}, "variant_tax_code": {"type": "text", "index": 54, "name": "variant_tax_code", "comment": "This parameter applies only to the stores that have the Avalara AvaTax app installed. Specifies the Avalara tax code for the product variant."}, "variant_created_at": {"type": "timestamp without time zone", "index": 55, "name": "variant_created_at", "comment": "The date and time (ISO 8601 format) when the product variant was created."}, "variant_updated_at": {"type": "timestamp without time zone", "index": 56, "name": "variant_updated_at", "comment": "The date and time when the product variant was last modified. Gets returned in ISO 8601 format."}, "variant_is_available_for_sale": {"type": "boolean", "index": 57, "name": "variant_is_available_for_sale", "comment": "Indicates whether the product variant is available for sale."}, "variant_display_name": {"type": "text", "index": 58, "name": "variant_display_name", "comment": "The display name of the variant, based on the product's title and variant's title."}, "variant_legacy_resource_id": {"type": "integer", "index": 59, "name": "variant_legacy_resource_id", "comment": "The ID of the corresponding resource in the REST Admin API."}, "variant_has_components_required": {"type": "boolean", "index": 60, "name": "variant_has_components_required", "comment": "Indicates whether a product variant requires components."}, "variant_sellable_online_quantity": {"type": "integer", "index": 61, "name": "variant_sellable_online_quantity", "comment": "The total sellable quantity of the variant for online channels."}, "variant_metafield_bea81c1795a612d8fc3a232b156467c1_extra_field": {"type": "text", "index": 62, "name": "variant_metafield_bea81c1795a612d8fc3a232b156467c1_extra_field", "comment": null}, "variant_metafield_bea81c1795a612d8fc3a232b156467c1_gterwbvre": {"type": "text", "index": 63, "name": "variant_metafield_bea81c1795a612d8fc3a232b156467c1_gterwbvre", "comment": null}, "subtotal_sold": {"type": "double precision", "index": 64, "name": "subtotal_sold", "comment": "Total amount (monetary, in shop currency) sold from the inventory level. Includes refunds."}, "quantity_sold": {"type": "bigint", "index": 65, "name": "quantity_sold", "comment": "Total quantity sold from the inventory level. Includes refunds."}, "count_distinct_orders": {"type": "bigint", "index": 66, "name": "count_distinct_orders", "comment": "The number of distinct orders placed from this inventory level."}, "count_distinct_customers": {"type": "bigint", "index": 67, "name": "count_distinct_customers", "comment": "The number of distinct customers (based on customer_id) that have placed orders against this inventory level."}, "count_distinct_customer_emails": {"type": "bigint", "index": 68, "name": "count_distinct_customer_emails", "comment": "The number of distinct customer emails that have placed orders against this inventory level."}, "first_order_timestamp": {"type": "timestamp without time zone", "index": 69, "name": "first_order_timestamp", "comment": "The timetamp of the first order against this inventory level."}, "last_order_timestamp": {"type": "timestamp without time zone", "index": 70, "name": "last_order_timestamp", "comment": "The timestamp of the first order against this inventory level."}, "subtotal_sold_refunds": {"type": "double precision", "index": 71, "name": "subtotal_sold_refunds", "comment": "The monetary amount (in shop currency) of inventory level goods that have been refunded."}, "quantity_sold_refunds": {"type": "double precision", "index": 72, "name": "quantity_sold_refunds", "comment": "The quantity of inventory level goods that have been refunded."}, "count_fulfillment_pending": {"type": "bigint", "index": 73, "name": "count_fulfillment_pending", "comment": "Count of currently pending distinct fulfillments for this inventory level. \"Pending\" = Shopify has created the fulfillment and is waiting for the third-party fulfillment service to transition it to 'open' or 'success'.\n"}, "count_fulfillment_open": {"type": "bigint", "index": 74, "name": "count_fulfillment_open", "comment": "Count of currently open distinct fulfillments for this inventory level. \"Open\" = The fulfillment has been acknowledged by the service and is in processing.\n"}, "count_fulfillment_success": {"type": "bigint", "index": 75, "name": "count_fulfillment_success", "comment": "Count of successful distinct fulfillments for this inventory level. \"Success\" = The fulfillment was successful.\n"}, "count_fulfillment_cancelled": {"type": "bigint", "index": 76, "name": "count_fulfillment_cancelled", "comment": "Count of cancelled distinct fulfillments for this inventory level. \"Cancelled\" = The fulfillment was cancelled.\n"}, "count_fulfillment_error": {"type": "bigint", "index": 77, "name": "count_fulfillment_error", "comment": "Count of distinct fulfillments for this inventory level that encountered an error. \"Error\" = There was an error with the fulfillment request.\n"}, "count_fulfillment_failure": {"type": "bigint", "index": 78, "name": "count_fulfillment_failure", "comment": "Count of distinct fulfillments for this inventory level that failed. \"Failure\" = The fulfillment request failed.\n"}, "incoming_quantity": {"type": "bigint", "index": 79, "name": "incoming_quantity", "comment": "The incoming quantity on its way to a merchant's location. Returns null if the inventory item is not tracked."}, "on_hand_quantity": {"type": "bigint", "index": 80, "name": "on_hand_quantity", "comment": "The total number of units that are physically at a location. The `on_hand` state equals the sum of inventory quantities that  are in the `available`, `committed`, `reserved`, `damaged`, `safety_stock`, and `quality_control` states. Returns null if the inventory item is not tracked.\n"}, "available_quantity": {"type": "bigint", "index": 81, "name": "available_quantity", "comment": "The available quantity that a merchant can sell, determined by coalescing the `quantity` where  inventory_state_name = 'available' from `stg_shopify_gql__inventory_quantity`and `available_quantity`  from the deprecated `stg_shopify_gql__inventory_level`. Returns null if the inventory item is not tracked.\n"}, "committed_quantity": {"type": "bigint", "index": 82, "name": "committed_quantity", "comment": "The number of units that are part of a placed order but aren't fulfilled. When a draft order is created, the inventory isn't committed until the draft order is completed and an order is created. Returns null if the inventory item is not tracked."}, "reserved_quantity": {"type": "bigint", "index": 83, "name": "reserved_quantity", "comment": "The on-hand units that are temporarily set aside. Returns null if the inventory item is not tracked."}, "damaged_quantity": {"type": "bigint", "index": 84, "name": "damaged_quantity", "comment": "The on-hand units that aren't sellable or usable due to damage. Returns null if the inventory item is not tracked."}, "safety_stock_quantity": {"type": "bigint", "index": 85, "name": "safety_stock_quantity", "comment": "The on-hand units that are set aside to help guard against overselling. Returns null if the inventory item is not tracked."}, "quality_control_quantity": {"type": "bigint", "index": 86, "name": "quality_control_quantity", "comment": "The on-hand units that aren't sellable because they're currently in inspection for quality purposes. Returns 